fullName: Test Suites.Page Homepage.Verify Homepage Reseplanerare Is Visible and Returns HTTP Status Code STATUS_OK (200)
description:

1. Verify that Reseplanerare is visible
2. Send a GET request to JLT homepage Reseplanerare.
3. Verify that the received HTTP status code is 200.
